### =========================================================
### Employee Management CAP Backend - Consolidated Test File
### Service Base URL
### =========================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4004/employee


### =========================================================
### 1. Service Document and Metadata
### =========================================================

### Service Document
GET {{baseUrl}}


### Metadata
GET {{baseUrl}}/$metadata


### =========================================================
### 2. Master Data Read Tests
### =========================================================

### Get all Departments
GET {{baseUrl}}/Departments


### Get all Company Laptops
GET {{baseUrl}}/CompanyLaptops


### Get all Skills
GET {{baseUrl}}/Skills


### Get all Employee Skill Assignments
GET {{baseUrl}}/EmployeeSkillAssignments


### Get all Employees
GET {{baseUrl}}/Employees


### =========================================================
### 3. Read Employees with Associations
### =========================================================

### Get Employees with Department
GET {{baseUrl}}/Employees?$expand=department


### Get Employees with Laptop
GET {{baseUrl}}/Employees?$expand=laptop


### Get Employees with Skill Assignments
GET {{baseUrl}}/Employees?$expand=skillAssignments


### Get Employees with Skill Assignments and Skill Master Data
GET {{baseUrl}}/Employees?$expand=skillAssignments($expand=skill)


### Get Employees with Department, Laptop and Skills
GET {{baseUrl}}/Employees?$expand=department,laptop,skillAssignments($expand=skill)


### =========================================================
### 4. Normal CRUDQ Create Employee - Validation Tests
### This will trigger before CREATE Employees handler
### =========================================================

### Create Employee - Missing Name
POST {{baseUrl}}/Employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "missing.name@company.com",
  "designation": "Developer",
  "salary": 45000,
  "department_ID": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111"
}


### Create Employee - Missing Email
POST {{baseUrl}}/Employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Missing Email Employee",
  "designation": "Developer",
