### 12. Onboard Employee - No Available Laptop Scenario
### Run this only after all laptops are already ASSIGNED
### =========================================================

### Check Available Laptops
GET {{baseUrl}}/CompanyLaptops?$filter=status eq 'AVAILABLE'


### Onboard Employee - Expected to Fail if No Laptop Available
